> [[collapsible show="Author Commentary" hide="Close Thy Ramblings"]]
> I ended up writing this for JamCon-2021. It was pretty fun to write this, but if I'm being honest, I half expected this to float to the bottom of the sea with twenty downvotes as the anchor. But, I was pleasantly surprised. 
> 
> This was inspired by the Loch Ness Monster; in fact, the original draft was to revamp the idea of it and turn it into an eldritch horror that it was only discovered on Parawatch, not the irl events. But, I ended up changing it around.
> 
> My first parawatch tale, though. Pretty cool.
> [[/collapsible]]
